      "webPublicationDate":"2013-11-01T08:56:32Z",
      "webTitle":"More young women trapped in low-paid, low-skilled jobs",
      "webUrl":"http://www.theguardian.com/business/2013/nov/01/young-women-trapped-low-paid-skilled-jobs",
